"                wind-driven waves. The model estimates the energy of both wave\n"
"                types at each point, and uses the larger value to represent\n"
"                wave energies at that point. Wind-driven waves tend to dominate\n"
"                in areas sheltered from the open ocean. If sheltered points\n"
"                appear dominated by ocean waves, the max fetch distance may be\n"
"                too short.\n"
