msgstr ""

#: src/natcap/invest/urban_nature_access/urban_nature_access.py:420
msgid "Positive pixel values indicate an oversupply of urban nature for the population group POP_GROUP relative to the stated urban nature demand. Negative values indicate an undersupply of urban nature for the population group POP_GROUP relative to the stated urban nature demand."
